<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Letter - {{companyName}}</title>
    <!-- Use similar fonts to the reference (Helvetica/Arial sans-serif stack, or Inter) -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Montserrat:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #2c323f;
            -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            print-color-adjust: exact;
            font-size: 11px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .a4-container {
            width: 210mm;
            min-height: 297mm;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Top Banner Vector Graphics */
        .top-banner {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 210mm;
            height: 45mm;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Bottom Banner Vector Graphics */
        .bottom-banner {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 210mm;
            height: 25mm;
            z-index: 1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .header-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            width: 100%;
            height: 45mm;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .header-title {
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-left: 20mm;
            margin-top: 5mm;
        }

        .header-logo {
            margin-right: 15mm;
            margin-top: 5mm;
            text-align: right;
            color: #0c2049;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        .header-logo-icon {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #008f87;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .header-logo-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-top: 2px;
        }

        /* Main Body Layer */
        .content-layer {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 10mm 20mm 25mm 20mm;
        }

        /* Meta Section (To & Date) */
        .meta-section {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #2c323f;
        }

        .recipient-info {
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .recipient-label {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .recipient-name {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #2c323f;
        }
        
        .recipient-address {
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .date-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #2c323f;
        }

        /* Intro Paragraph */
        .intro-text {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .intro-text p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        /* Two Column Layout */
        .columns-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .col-left {
            width: 48%;
        }

        .col-right {
            width: 48%;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c323f;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        /* Position Details Table */
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .details-table tr {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #7cb3c8;
        }
        .details-table tr:last-child {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #7cb3c8;
        }
        .details-table td {
            padding: 8px 0;
            font-size: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }
        .details-table td.label-cell {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a2a40;
            width: 45%;
        }
        .details-table td.value-cell {
            color: #3a4a5f;
            text-align: right;
        }

        /* Key Responsibilities List */
        .responsibilities-intro {
            font-size: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .responsibilities-list {
            padding-left: 15px;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .responsibilities-list li {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .responsibilities-outro {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Additional Sections */
        .extra-section {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .extra-section p {
            margin-bottom: 4px;
            color: #333;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #7cb3c8;
            margin: 25px 0 20px 0;
        }

        /* Signature and Footer Area */
        .bottom-area {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .signature-block {
            width: 50%;
        }
        
        .closure-text {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .sender-name {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #2c323f;
        }

        .sender-title {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .contact-info {
            width: 45%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 12px;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .contact-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: flex-end;
            gap: 8px;
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .contact-icon {
            width: 16px;
            height: 16px;
            background: #008f87;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 8px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="a4-container">
        
        <!-- Top SVG Banner -->
        <svg class="top-banner" viewBox="0 0 800 170" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- Light Blue Abstract Angle -->
            <polygon points="0,0 800,0 800,105 0,170" fill="#ccdae6" />
            <!-- Teal Middle Angle -->
            <polygon points="0,0 580,0 480,140 0,150" fill="#008f87" />
            <!-- Dark Navy Main Shape -->
            <polygon points="0,0 520,0 350,140 0,140" fill="#0c2049" />
            <!-- Decorative Light Blue Stripes -->
            <polygon points="150,140 200,140 240,165 190,165" fill="#68c0b5" />
            <polygon points="210,140 260,140 300,165 250,165" fill="#008f87" />
            
            <!-- Abstract circle hash pattern on top right inside navy -->
            <g transform="translate(540, 20) rotate(45)" opacity="0.8">
                <line x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="40" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" />
                <line x1="8" y1="-5" x2="8" y2="45" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" />
                <line x1="16" y1="-10" x2="16" y2="50" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" />
                <line x1="24" y1="-5" x2="24" y2="45" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" />
                <line x1="32" y1="0" x2="32" y2="40" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" />
            </g>
        </svg>

        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="header-title">APPOINTMENT LETTER</div>
            <div class="header-logo">
                <div class="header-logo-icon">§</div>
                <div class="header-logo-text">{{#if companyName}}{{companyName}}{{else}}COMPANY{{/if}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-layer">
            
            <div class="meta-section">
                <div class="recipient-info">
                    <div class="recipient-label">To:</div>
                    <div class="recipient-name">{{employeeName}}</div>
                    {{#if employeeAddress}}
                    <div class="recipient-address">{{{employeeAddress}}}</div>
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="date-text">{{#if appointmentDate}}{{appointmentDate}}{{else}}{{date}}{{/if}}</div>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-text">
                <p>Dear {{#if employeeName}}{{employeeName}}{{else}}Candidate{{/if}},</p>
                <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been officially appointed to the position of <strong>{{position}}</strong>, effective <strong>{{#if startDate}}{{startDate}}{{else}}{{appointmentDate}}{{/if}}</strong>, within the <strong>{{department}}</strong> Department of {{companyName}}.</p>
                <p>Your appointment reflects the company's confidence in your capabilities, work ethic, and consistent contributions to operational excellence and your ongoing commitment to improving team performance.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="columns-container">
                <!-- Left Column -->
                <div class="col-left">
                    <div class="section-title">1. Position Details</div>
                    <table class="details-table">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label-cell">Position Title</td>
                            <td class="value-cell">{{position}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label-cell">Department</td>
                            <td class="value-cell">{{department}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label-cell">Reporting To</td>
                            <td class="value-cell">{{#if reportingTo}}{{reportingTo}}{{else}}Department Head{{/if}}</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label-cell">Employment Type</td>
                            <td class="value-cell">Full-Time</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td class="label-cell">Start Date</td>
                            <td class="value-cell">{{#if startDate}}{{startDate}}{{else}}{{appointmentDate}}{{/if}}</td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Column -->
                <div class="col-right">
                    <div class="section-title">2. Key Responsibilities</div>
                    <div class="responsibilities-intro">You will be responsible for:</div>
                    <ul class="responsibilities-list">
                        {{#if keyResponsibilities}}
                            {{#each keyResponsibilities}}
                                <li>{{this}}</li>
                            {{/each}}
                        {{else}}
                            <li>Leading daily workflow within your designated department.</li>
                            <li>Overseeing report accuracy, analysis quality, and operational improvements.</li>
                            <li>Supporting audit cycles and cross-functional initiatives.</li>
                            <li>Ensuring all processes comply with standard internal SOPs and Indian Labour Codes.</li>
                        {{/if}}
                    </ul>
                    <div class="responsibilities-outro">Additional responsibilities may be assigned as needed to support strategic goals.</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extra-section">
                <div class="section-title">3. Compensation &amp; Benefits</div>
                <p>Your compensation package including Fixed Pay and performance-linked benefits sums to <strong>{{#if salaryInWords}}₹{{salary}} ({{salaryInWords}}){{else}}₹{{salary}} per annum{{/if}}</strong>. Applicable deductions like PF, ESI, and taxes will be processed as per prevailing Indian laws. Detailed structure will be communicated separately by the Human Resources Department.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="extra-section">
                <div class="section-title">4. Confirmation of Appointment</div>
                <p>Please sign and return the acknowledgment section below within 5 working days to confirm your acceptance of this appointment.</p>
                <p>We look forward to your continued leadership and meaningful contributions to the company's future growth. Congratulations on your new role.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <div class="bottom-area">
                <div class="signature-block">
                    <div class="closure-text">Sincerely,</div>
                    <div class="sender-name">{{#if hrContactPerson}}{{hrContactPerson}}{{else}}HR Director{{/if}}</div>
                    <div class="sender-title">Human Resources Department</div>
                </div>

                <div class="contact-info">
                    {{#if companyPhone}}
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">✆</div>
                        <div>{{companyPhone}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div class="contact-item">
                        <div class="contact-icon">📍</div>
                        <div>{{#if companyAddress}}{{{companyAddress}}}{{else}}Corporate Headquarters{{/if}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Bottom SVG Banner -->
        <svg class="bottom-banner" viewBox="0 0 800 95" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <!-- Light Blue Abstract Angle -->
            <polygon points="400,95 800,95 800,20 600,95" fill="#ccdae6" />
            <!-- Teal Angles -->
            <polygon points="500,95 650,95 800,40 800,70" fill="#008f87" />
            <polygon points="680,95 760,95 800,80 800,95" fill="#68c0b5" />
            <!-- Dark Navy Main Shape -->
            <polygon points="0,95 600,95 500,60 0,60" fill="#0c2049" />
            
            <!-- Diagonal stripes on the teal part -->
            <polygon points="550,95 580,95 640,75 610,75" fill="#ffffff" />
            <polygon points="610,95 640,95 700,70 670,70" fill="#ffffff" />
        </svg>

    </div>
</body>
</html>